ointing a new member to RERA", "para": "The Odisha government has begun appointing a new member to the Real Estate Regulatory Authority. This appointment follows the earlier departure of the previous administration member. The chairperson's post at the Odisha Real Estate Appellate Tribunal also remains vacant. Stakeholders express concerns about delays affecting dispute resolution processes. Timely appointments are crucial for consumer protection and sector confidence.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/rera/odisha-government-moves-to-appoint-new-member-to-orera-amidst-key-vacancies/132452405?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-141834/132452405.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "rera"}]}